### Track Concept Evolution - Transformer Paper
# This request tracks the evolution of the transformer concept starting from
# the famous "Attention Is All You Need" paper (1706.03762)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/track
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seed_paper_ids": ["1706.03762"],
  "end_date": "2017-12-31",
  "window_months": 6,
  "max_papers_per_window": 200
}

